System.out.println(policy.getType());

🧠 Real use:-
System decide karta hai kaise evaluate kare
Reporting category
--------------------------------
Policy policy = new Policy();

policy.setId("POL-001");
policy.setName("Dev-Prod Conflict");
policy.setDescription("Developer should not have Production access");
policy.setType("SoD");

System.out.println(policy.getId());
System.out.println(policy.getName());
System.out.println(policy.getDescription());
System.out.println(policy.getType());
✅ Output:-
POL-001
Dev-Prod Conflict
Developer should not have Production access
SoD
